#. </p><hr><p><a class="sc" id="39"></a><a class="pts-cs" id="bu-ss.4.4.6"></a><a class="ms-pa" id="ms-pa1218"></a><a class="pts-vp-en" id="bd.1.228"></a> 
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss4:pts-cs4.6.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena aññatarā itthī kulūpakaṃ bhikkhuṃ etadavoca—"
msgstr "On one occasion a woman said to a monk who was supported by her family,"

msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss4:pts-cs4.6.2"
msgid "“kathāhaṃ, bhante, sugatiṃ gaccheyyan”ti?"
msgstr "“Venerable, how can I get a good rebirth?”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss4:pts-cs4.6.3"
msgid "“Tena hi, bhagini, aggadānaṃ dehī”ti."
msgstr "“Well, Sister, give the highest gift.”"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "pli-tv-bu-vb-ss4:pts-cs4.6.4"
msgid "“Kiṃ, bhante, aggadānan”ti?"
msgstr "“What’s the highest gift?”"

